# pytest-yml

pytest plugin for generating test cases by yaml


## Install
```
pip install pytest-yaml-sanmu
```


## Config
```ini
[pytest]
run_yaml_case = 1
```


## Usage
```
(venv) D:\git\github\dongfangtianyu\pytest-yaml-sanmu>pytest
